  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Vavuniya District Hospital health workers protest",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A demonstration was carried out today (27) by health workers of Vavuniya District Hospital.",
        "This demonstration has been carried out demanding that fuel should be provided at a separate fuel filling station on a special day for health workers.",
        "In the past, operations were carried out to get fuel at a separate fuel filling station for the hospital staff on special days.",
        "However, this operation has been stopped for the past few days and they now have to go through the public queue to get fuel and thus they have to face difficulties in going to their duty on time.",
        "Also, the protestors have said that the situation should be changed and steps should be taken to provide fuel on a separate day and if this situation continues, they will go on strike."
      ],
